\text{where }x=r\sin\theta\cos\phi\text{, }y=r\sin\theta\sin\phi\text{, and }z=r\cos\theta.\text{ Find determinants }\det{(A)}\text{, }\det{(A^{-1})}\text{, and }\det{(A^2)}.
